{"id":359,"date":"2018-05-28T16:29:39","date_gmt":"2018-05-28T16:29:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/perfecttravelsandalteva\/"},"modified":"2023-03-22T19:51:10","modified_gmt":"2023-03-22T19:51:10","slug":"perfecttravelsandalteva","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/perfecttravelsandalteva\/","title":{"rendered":"Traveling Southeast Asia With Teva | The Perfect Travel Sandal?"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\" data-animation-override=\"\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527421276788-XUBWFODI77WIRVPLQ1J3\/tevasoutheastasia\" alt=\"tevasoutheastasia\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527421276788-XUBWFODI77WIRVPLQ1J3\/tevasoutheastasia\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x2501\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5b0a992a575d1fdde9780b21\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\" data-animation-override=\"\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527421135499-ND8IDY8V4VO34HV6UL7J\/tevasoutheastasia\" alt=\"tevasoutheastasia\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527421135499-ND8IDY8V4VO34HV6UL7J\/tevasoutheastasia\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x1817\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5b0a98a1758d461b37d4c0ff\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>WHY SOUTHEAST ASIA?&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>I&#8217;ve spent the past 2 months traveling Southeast Asia. I&#8217;ve visited Thailand, Cambodia, and Vietnam so far. It&#8217;s been a whirlwind of an experience.<\/p>\n<p>I initially set out to visit Southeast Asia a year ago. I wanted it to be the first stop on<a href=\"http:\/\/www.heyciara.com\/blog\/pjd1p2b8ax1owkm65abfdgk56rnf0q\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> my &#8217;round the world trip<\/a> because everyone raved about it. Thanks to delicious food, budget accommodation, rich culture, and developed tourism infrastructure, Southeast Asia is known as the ultimate backpacker&#8217;s destination.<\/p>\n<p>Ya girl was on a budget, so the cheap prices in this region were definitely appealing. Ultimately, I ended up <a href=\"http:\/\/www.heyciara.com\/blog\/here-is-what-really-went-down-on-my-solo-trip-through-latin-america-after-quitting-my-job\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">traveling Latin America instead<\/a>, but I&#8217;m happy to finally visit this part of the world.<\/p>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\" data-animation-override=\"\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527419949822-PFH0UB2418O0D4VFZFZR\/tevasoutheastasia\" alt=\"tevasoutheastasia\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527419949822-PFH0UB2418O0D4VFZFZR\/tevasoutheastasia\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x2500\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5b0a9400758d461b37d4710c\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">&#8220;We go anywhere, do anything, and live for the unscripted moments that make the best memories&#8221; &#8211; Teva<\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\" data-animation-override=\"\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527421015410-IF760BD6GJUOZ411XXI8\/tevasoutheastasia\" alt=\"tevasoutheastasia\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527421015410-IF760BD6GJUOZ411XXI8\/tevasoutheastasia\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x1665\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5b0a981a575d1fdde977f7a5\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>For the most part, everyone was right about Southeast Asia.&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>I&#8217;ve fallen in love with Pad Thai, spicy Pho,&nbsp;and unidentifiable food served from street stalls.<\/p>\n<p>I&#8217;ve stepped foot on what might be the most perfect beach in the world.<\/p>\n<p>I&#8217;ve slept in beds that cost less than a cup of coffee.<\/p>\n<p>I&#8217;ve explored ancient temples that blew my mind.<\/p>\n<p>I&#8217;ve discovered a new love for cozy cafes hidden in busy alleys.<\/p>\n<p>I&#8217;ve frolicked alongside elephants in the jungle.<\/p>\n<p>I&#8217;ve eaten fruit that I didn&#8217;t know existed.<\/p>\n<p>I&#8217;ve risked it all on the back of motorbikes.<\/p>\n<p>I&#8217;ve stayed in a Cambodian family&#8217;s home.<\/p>\n<p>I swam in a bioluminescent beach. It was magical.<\/p>\n<p>The best part? My trip isn&#8217;t over just yet.<\/p>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\" data-animation-override=\"\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527423811859-CP47TOUO4KG178SMC8A0\/tevasoutheastasia\" alt=\"tevasoutheastasia\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527423811859-CP47TOUO4KG178SMC8A0\/tevasoutheastasia\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x3349\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5b0aa300758d461b37d5956e\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\" data-animation-override=\"\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527423708094-STVOYJIGXGI9MPV1MVGA\/tevasoutheastasia\" alt=\"tevasoutheastasia\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527423708094-STVOYJIGXGI9MPV1MVGA\/tevasoutheastasia\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x2624\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5b0aa2b78a922dbfa24f0918\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\" data-animation-override=\"\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527424038028-PXG52R09DYMF8AB4F0H2\/tevasoutheastasia\" alt=\"tevasoutheastasia\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527424038028-PXG52R09DYMF8AB4F0H2\/tevasoutheastasia\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x1664\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5b0aa37f562fa7e07bec649e\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>TRAVELING WITH TEVA<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>I bought my first pair of Tevas for <a href=\"http:\/\/www.heyciara.com\/blog\/costa-rica-packing-tips-list\">a trip to Costa Rica<\/a>. It was my <a href=\"http:\/\/www.heyciara.com\/blog\/what-i-gained-from-my-first-solo-trip-abroad\">first solo trip <\/a>abroad and I wanted to be prepared for ALL OF THE THINGS. You know how it goes. Anyway,&nbsp;I knew Costa Rica was full of <a href=\"http:\/\/www.heyciara.com\/blog\/10-things-to-cross-off-your-bucketlist-in-costa-rica\">waterfalls, river, volcanos, and beaches<\/a>. I heard that Tevas would be the perfect waterproof shoes to wear while exploring the country. Despite them looking like shoes for an <strong>American adventure dad<\/strong>, I bought a pair and I fell in love with them.<\/p>\n<p>Over a year later, I&#8217;m proud to collaborate with <a href=\"https:\/\/www.teva.com\/best-travel-shoes\/\">Teva<\/a> on this blog post. They sent me their <a href=\"https:\/\/www.teva.com\/women-sandals\/hurricane-xlt2\/1019235.html?dwvar_1019235_color=LGBE#q=hurricane&amp;start=2&amp;cgid\">Hurricane XLT 2<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.teva.com\/women-sandals\/original-universal\/1003987.html#q=originals&amp;start=1&amp;cgid\">Original Universal<\/a>, and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.teva.com\/women-sandals\/midform-universal\/1090969.html#start=109&amp;cgid=women-new-arrivals\">Midform Universal<\/a>,&nbsp;which have been perfect while traveling Southeast Asia. I&#8217;ve worn them while walking on rocky beaches, exploring busy markets, and bathing beautiful elephants. They&#8217;re sturdy yet lightweight, and easy to adjust. It&#8217;s so difficult to find cute adventure shoes\/sandals, but Teva has a wide range of colorful and fun sandals.<\/p>\n<p>I&#8217;m grateful for the chance to partner with a company that I use and love. It also helps that they&#8217;ve given me complete creative freedom. A year ago, I was so nervous about quitting my job to travel the world. On that first trip to Costa Rica, I was unsure about what my future would hold. I don&#8217;t have it all figured out, but it&#8217;s such a blessing to be able to inspire others to see the world and live life on their own terms. Partnering with Teva has shown me that everything eventually comes full circle.<\/p>\n<div class=\"product-block\">\n<div class=\"image-container\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Teva-Womens-Original-Universal-Miramar\/dp\/B01IPXQWUU?psc=1&amp;SubscriptionId=AKIAIOCEBIGP6NUBL47A&amp;tag=heyciara05-20&amp;linkCode=xm2&amp;camp=2025&amp;creative=165953&amp;creativeASIN=B01IPXQWUU\" target=\"new\" rel=\"noopener\"><br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/4179JfT-uDL.jpg\"><br \/>\n<\/a><\/div>\n<div class=\"productDetails center\">\n<p><a class=\"buy-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Teva-Womens-Original-Universal-Miramar\/dp\/B01IPXQWUU?psc=1&amp;SubscriptionId=AKIAIOCEBIGP6NUBL47A&amp;tag=heyciara05-20&amp;linkCode=xm2&amp;camp=2025&amp;creative=165953&amp;creativeASIN=B01IPXQWUU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-animation-role=\"button\"><br \/>\n<span class=\"sqs-amazon-button sqs-system-button sqs-editable-button sqs-button-element--primary\"><br \/>\nBuy on Amazon<br \/>\n<\/span><br \/>\n<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\" data-animation-override=\"\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527429513188-MCPLM0PMCL6Z4C5K0H13\/tevasoutheastasia\" alt=\"tevasoutheastasia\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527429513188-MCPLM0PMCL6Z4C5K0H13\/tevasoutheastasia\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x2518\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5b0ab94770a6addca9bad395\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\" data-animation-override=\"\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527429362203-3MWPUBCGAB3VTSYMR815\/tevasoutheastasia\" alt=\"tevasoutheastasia\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1527429362203-3MWPUBCGAB3VTSYMR815\/tevasoutheastasia\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x3125\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5b0ab88a562fa7e07bee4048\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animati